<item>
            <title>[LU-928] Update or improvement to a code comment</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-928</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This Jira issue should be used as the tracker for any changes to the Lustre code comments.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When pushing to git include &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-928&quot; title=&quot;Update or improvement to a code comment&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-928&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-928&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; as the Jira ticket number and ensure that your commit comment fully describes the comment change, in many cases the commit comment will be the new or revised text of the Lustre code comment itself.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that this tracker is exclusively to be used against changes to the Lustre code comments, it is not to be used to track changes to code layout, or white space changes etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
